				<td colspan="2"><span>Steppy, you will probably see better immediate results by capping out JF, then SM, then the GoD IM and SMs.  EN first vs SM/IM/JF first boils down to this:
<br />
Do I want to hit a lot of folks (everyone paying attention at least) with the best possible Bard buffs possible?
<br />
or
<br />
Do I want to hit EVERYONE (afks and Bots included) with lesser quality buffs.
<br />
